API 명세서

-게시판(bid-보드아이디(1.설명소개서 2.공지사항 3.Q&A게시판), aid-게시글아이디, cid-댓글아이디)
1. api/list/:bid
2. api/list/:bid/:aid
3. api/list/:bid/create
4. api/list/:bid/:aid/delete
5. api/list/:bid/:aid/edit
6. api/list/:bid/:aid/comment/create
7. api/list/:bid/:aid/:cid/edit
8. api/list/:bid/:aid/:cid/delete

-멘토방(rid->mentoroom_id)
1. api/mentoroom - 멘토방목록
2. api/mentoroom/create - 멘토신청
3. api/mentoroom/:rid - 멘토방
4. api/mentoroom/:rid/menti_join - 멘티신청
5. api/mentoroom/:rid/menti_canceal - 멘티신청취소
6. api/mentoroom/:rid/report/upload - 보고서 제출
7. api/mentoroom/:rid/report/download - 보고서 다운로드
8. api/mentoroom/:rid/confirm - 멘토신청승인
9. api/mentoroom/:rid/reject - 멘토승인거절

-관리자(auth->user_auth(1.멘토 2.멘티 3.관리자))
1. api/admin/user/:auth - 사용자목록
2. api/admin/room_info - 멘토방 설정
3. api/admin/mentoroom - 멘토방 목록
4. api/admin/report - 보고서목록
5. api/admin/survey - 설문조사